<div class="page main-page">
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h2 class="page-title" style="margin:0;">主页</h2>
        <button id="fab-add" class="btn-fab">+</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">推荐内容</div>
        <p>这里是主页的主要内容区域，使用黑白灰色调，强调色为红色。</p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" style="background-color: #f44336;">红色按钮</button>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="page main-page">
    <!-- 帖子列表容器 -->
    <div id="posts-container" class="posts-container">
        <!-- 帖子卡片会动态生成 -->
    </div>
    <!-- 加载提示 -->
    <div id="loading-indicator" style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; display: none;">加载中...</div>
    <!-- 没有更多提示 -->
    <div id="no-more-posts" style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #757575; display: none;">没有更多文章了</div>
</div>

<!-- 图片预览模态框 -->
<div id="image-modal" class="image-modal" style="display:none;">
    <span class="image-close" onclick="closeImageModal()">&times;</span>
    <img class="image-modal-content" id="modal-image">
</div>